-- Regions Financial to Sell Morgan Keegan
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-01-11T21:34:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-11/regions-financial-to-sell-morgan-keegan.html
Regions Financial Corp. (RF)  said it
agreed to sell Morgan Keegan & Co. and related affiliates to
 Raymond James Financial Inc. (RJF)  for $930 million.  Morgan Keegan will also pay Regions a dividend of $250
million before closing, pending regulatory approval, resulting
in total proceeds of $1.18 billion to Regions.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  